 /**
- * Diverg — Solana token bundle scanner.
- * Architecture — standard on-chain bundle detection flow:
- *   1. getAsset → token name/symbol/supply/decimals
- *   2. getTokenAccounts (DAS, paginated) → sorted holders
- *   3. getSignaturesForAddress (RPC) → oldest sig per holder (concurrent)
- *   4. /v0/transactions batch parse → infer first SOL funder per holder
- *   5. batch-identity → label funders
- *   6. group by funder, filter exchanges → suspicious clusters
- *   7. compute verdict + risk score
+ * Solana bundle snapshot — runs entirely in the extension (Helius BYOK).
+ * Parity with Sectester investigation/solana_bundle.py + solana_bundle_signals.py:
+ * DAS getTokenAccounts (paginated holders), largest-accounts fallback, LP skip, up to 120 wallets,
+ * 2-hop ultimate-funder clustering, parallel Helius fetches, deeper coordination defaults.
